protognome (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Flutter-based GNOME-native Proton compatibility tool manager.
  * Fork of ProtonUp-Qt with native GNOME UI (no KDE dependencies).
  * SQLite backend for caching release lists and game data.
  * New feature: Apply a single Proton version to ALL Steam games at once.
  * Supports GE-Proton, Boxtron, Luxtorpeda, SteamTinkerLaunch.

 -- ProtoGNOME Contributors <protognome@example.com>  Mon, 23 Feb 2026 21:00:00 +0000
